T1  - THE WELFARE EFFECTS OF MANDATORY REEMPLOYMENT PROGRAMS: COMBINING A STRUCTURAL MODEL AND EXPERIMENTAL DATA
AU  - Maibom, Jonas
Y1  - 2023/05/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12621
T2  - International Economic Review
