T1  - VACCINE HESITANCY, PASSPORTS, AND THE DEMAND FOR VACCINATION
AU  - Gans, Joshua S.
Y1  - 2023/05/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12609
T2  - International Economic Review
