T1  - MONETARY POLICY AND INEQUALITY: HOW DOES ONE AFFECT THE OTHER?
AU  - Ma, Eunseong
Y1  - 2023/05/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12610
T2  - International Economic Review
